<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٢٣٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4563">عَلِيُّ بْنُ عَبْدِ اللهِ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2478">سُفْيَانُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5917">الزُّهْرِيُّ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2249">سَالِمٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">أَبِيهِ </a>عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">«إِذَا اسْتَأْذَنَتِ امْرَأَةُ أَحَدِكُمْ إِلَى الْمَسْجِدِ فَلَا يَمْنَعْهَا.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>